Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.02,0:20:29.06,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H868FD2&\pos(664,945)}軀體
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.02,0:20:29.06,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H868FD2&\pos(1675,953)}神的左手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.06,0:20:29.54,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn@微软雅黑\frz270\pos(1472,451)}啊 這是多麼慘酷的事情啊
