Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.42,0:20:36.82,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(757,341)}必須要削蘋果
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.42,0:20:36.82,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(762,564)}必須要快點做
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.42,0:20:36.82,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(963,961)}動畫編號 三百九十六
